\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
And I will make them lie down in safety.  
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
{\cf1 4}Hear the word of Jehovah, O Israelites,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\cf2\fs24 1}For Jehovah hath a charge against the inhabitants of the land,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
For there is no fidelity, nor true love,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
Nor knowledge of God in the land, 
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\cf2\fs24 2}But perjury, lying, and murder,
\par}

