Stealing, committing adultery, and deeds of violence,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
And acts of bloodshed quickly follow each other. 
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\cf2\fs24 3}Therefore the land mourns,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
And all its inhabitants languish,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
Together with the wild beasts and the birds of the heavens,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
While even the fish of the sea are swept away, 
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\cf2\fs24 3}Yet let none bring charges,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
And let none reprove,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
Since my people are but as their priestlings, 
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
