\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
Israel has behaved stubbornly,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
Can Jehovah now feed him,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
As he would a lamb in a broad pasture? 
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\cf2\fs24 17}Ephraim is wedded to idols; leave him alone! 
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\cf2\fs24 18}A band of topers! They gave themselves up to harlotry;
