{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
Since for you is the judgment.
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
 A snare have you become at Mizpeh,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
And a net spread out on Tabor, 
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\cf2\fs24 2}And a deep pit have they dug at Shittim,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
And there is no correction for any of them? 
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\cf2\fs24 3}I indeed know Ephraim,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
And Israel is not hid from me,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
For thou, O Ephraim, hast played the harlot,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
