{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
For the spirit of harlotry is within them,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
And Jehovah they do not know. 
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\cf2\fs24 5}Therefore Israel\uc1\u8217*s pride shall testify to his face,
