Judah also shall stumble with them. 
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\cf2\fs24 6}With their sheep and their cattle, they shall go about
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
To seek Jehovah, but shall not find him, 
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\cf2\fs24 7}For they have been untrue to Jehovah,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
Since they have begotten alien children;
