{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
In the day of punishment,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
Concerning the tribes of Israel I make known what is certain. 
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\cf2\fs24 10}The princes of Israel have become,
