{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
Like those who remove the landmarks;
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
Upon them I will pour out my wrath like water. 
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\cf2\fs24 11}Ephraim practises oppression and crushes right,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
For he is determined to go after vanity.
\par}

{\pard 
 
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\cf2\fs24 12}But I am like a moth to Ephraim,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
Like rottenness to the house of Israel; 
\par}

