{\super\cf2\fs24 13}For when Ephraim saw his sickness;
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
And Israel his sore,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
Ephraim went to Assyria
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
And Israel to the great king;
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
But he cannot heal you,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
Nor relieve you of your wound. 
\par}

